{
  "texts": [
    "The GPT4All dataset is utilized to train the GPT4All model, comprising approximately 740K English instructions.",
    "The construction process involves gathering questions from diverse domains through public datasets, invoking the model for responses, and subsequently performing operations such as semantic similarity-based deduplication of instructions and filtering out rejected model outputs.",
    "• GuanacoDataset foot_65.",
    "The GuanacoDataset, short for Generative Universal Assistant for Natural-language Adaptive Context-aware Omnilingual outputs Datasets, comprises approximately 534K instructions, spanning various languages such as English, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese (Taiwan), Traditional Chinese (Hong Kong), Japanese, German, and more.",
    "It provides different language versions based on 175 seed instructions."
  ]
}